{
	quest.01F59AF41A6DA0F7.quest_desc: ["&c致编辑模式用户:此任务已暂时隐藏,因为 &a飞龙奥法之镐&f 在撰写时没有合成配方.当 &a飞龙奥法之镐&f 可以通过 Forbidden Arcanus 或 KubeJS 制作时,请移除此注释并取消隐藏此任务.\\n&7[Note to those in Editing Mode: This quest was temporarily hidden as Draco Arcanus Pickaxe lacks a recipe at the time of writing. When Draco Arcanus Pickaxe becomes craftable, be it via Forbidden Arcanus or KubeJS, remove this note and unhide the quest.]&f"]
	quest.01F59AF41A6DA0F7.quest_subtitle: "等级:&54&7[Tier: 4]&f"
	quest.03E05018D64DDEE1.quest_desc: ["&e等级 5&r 基本上只用于 &aATM矿石&f,其他用途不多.\\n&7[Tier 5 is basically just for ATM Ore, not much else.]&f"]
