	quest.09733948CBCB3FB9.quest_desc: ["&d等级 6&r 是最高等级,任何可破坏的方块都可以用它挖掘,包括振金和难得素.\\n&7[Tier 6 is the highest tier, anything that is breakable can be mined with it, including 振金 and 难得素.]&f"]
